description:
This program is a free resource for immediate savings on prescription medications. Present your card with each prescription to the pharmacy at the time of purchase to receive your discount. Savings average 40% but can be as high as 75% on some generics. The card is really just like a reusable prescription coupon on all FDA approved medicines.

No eligibility or registration is required.
